sentences.sContent: He called this negative elemental particle the corpuscle.
sentences.sContent_eng: He called this negative elemental particle the corpuscle.
sentences.sCn: 他称之为这个负基本粒子叫做,微粒。

sentences.sContent: The nanometre corpuscle or nanometre material has its own special properties and new rules.
sentences.sContent_eng: The nanometre corpuscle or nanometre material has its own special properties and new rules.
sentences.sCn: 纳米微粒及纳米材料具有独特的性质和新的规律。

sentences.sContent: Know thyself , then, to be as a corpuscle, as a facet, as a characteristic, as a love, in the body of God.
sentences.sContent_eng: Know thyself , then, to be as a corpuscle, as a facet, as a characteristic, as a love, in the body of God.
sentences.sCn: 知道你自己在上帝的身体里成为一个微粒、一个小面、一种特性、一点爱。

trans.tranOther: one of the red or white cells in the blood
